/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n關鍵字：電視 落雨 選手平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依part真係睇到好爽<br />\n完全玩曬佢老板 同對面教練心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未睇過渡久地, 有冇LINK 呢下呢PART 有幾神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130510367c12f7d951f278ce1059c29091090b11","tid":181900,"uid":100861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"一直未出現21佢地班新人 蛭魔同栗田都係廢<br />\n咁就知邊個勁d"},{"pid":"6a3bb865ecc89e6f85850ada95d7495e0f9a38f7","tid":181900,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"蛭魔嘅智謀只限於球場內<br />\n同渡久地冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31114686e20f1dd91adf15f8ae3b71c3e7c30b7a","tid":181900,"uid":19496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蛭魔嘅智謀只限於球場內<br />\n同渡久地冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n回憶篇同世界盃，賭poker"},{"pid":"29aa4d8f6a88b7d4a1915f5e20004b83aa31dabc","tid":181900,"uid":30109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:48:42.000Z","msg":"我苦練左一年時間，終於快左0.1秒"},{"pid":"3efd8995e7a2f935763f0fdc9b2f524dc12ded99","tid":181900,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"渡久地係用一個新人既身份挑贏左成個日本球壇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9e25e7174eacabff41b265672a0b45a69d40d9","tid":181900,"uid":20899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:56:53.000Z","msg":"兩套漫畫定位唔同 有乜好比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ded7facca4f269d685119d590f0330bd671c00b","tid":181900,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又要搵翻掛機睇電視等落雨呢一part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n關鍵字：電視 落雨 選手平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依part真係睇到好爽<br />\n完全玩曬佢老板 同對面教練心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未睇過渡久地, 有冇LINK 呢下呢PART 有幾神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到渡久地開始受人注目<br />\n果場對手係班霸<br />\n而頭幾局渡久地失準失左十幾分<br />\n<br />\n因為佢失分就會輸錢畀老闆<br />\n而班霸可以刷得分數據<br />\n所以佢地都開心到彈起<br />\n<br />\n點知後尾發現好快會有暴雨<br />\n而渡久地係專登失咁多分黎DUMP波鐘搏取消球賽<br />\n所以班霸開始自製ERROR<br />\n希望盡快完局贏波<br />\n<br />\n但BASEBALL係睇數據既運動<br />\n要自製ERROR會令防守球員評價下降<br />\n所以班霸班投手就倒戈唔理自己教練戰術<br />\n希望落雨球賽取消<br />\n全隊士氣下降<br />\n<br />\n之後賽會宣佈球賽繼續<br />\n但班霸已經冇晒火<br />\n所以最後連失十幾分<br />\n<br />\n臨贏果一刻<br />\n渡久地挑釁對手教練話佢冇撚用<br />\n叫佢棄權<br />\n教練答允<br />\n根據賽會RULE<br />\n最後比賽評9:0<br />\n贏比賽之餘老闆都要輸錢"},{"pid":"df2c06efec947d3efa746e1b842de1e7dcd71cd9","tid":181900,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:01:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蛭魔=戰術+心理<br />\n渡久地除左依D  仲有投球技術</blockquote><br />\n講到蛭魔唔識投球咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   蛭魔可唔可以一個人屈柒對面成隊?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果一個人屈柒對面隊 咁仲有咩好睇？<br />\n加上衝鋒廿一個重心唔只係蛭魔<br />\n<br />\n利申 剩係有睇衝鋒廿一"},{"pid":"1e53b2366de173b6f718f192bd0ec390e796ff4e","tid":181900,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蛭魔嘅智謀只限於球場內<br />\n同渡久地冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n回憶篇同世界盃，賭poker</blockquote><br />\n你應該唔明我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7256d862c0180ce534ef963c448d97b796a97f8e","tid":181900,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又要搵翻掛機睇電視等落雨呢一part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n關鍵字：電視 落雨 選手平均分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依part真係睇到好爽<br />\n完全玩曬佢老板 同對面教練心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未睇過渡久地, 有冇LINK 呢下呢PART 有幾神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講到渡久地開始受人注目<br />\n果場對手係班霸<br />\n而頭幾局渡久地失準失左十幾分<br />\n<br />\n因為佢失分就會輸錢畀老闆<br />\n而班霸可以刷得分數據<br />\n所以佢地都開心到彈起<br />\n<br />\n點知後尾發現好快會有暴雨<br />\n而渡久地係專登失咁多分黎DUMP波鐘搏取消球賽<br />\n所以班霸開始自製ERROR<br />\n希望盡快完局贏波<br />\n<br />\n但BASEBALL係睇數據既運動<br />\n要自製ERROR會令防守球員評價下降<br />\n所以班霸班投手就倒戈唔理自己教練戰術<br />\n希望落雨球賽取消<br />\n全隊士氣下降<br />\n<br />\n之後賽會宣佈球賽繼續<br />\n但班霸已經冇晒火<br />\n所以最後連失十幾分<br />\n<br />\n臨贏果一刻<br />\n渡久地挑釁對手教練話佢冇撚用<br />\n叫佢棄權<br />\n教練答允<br />\n根據賽會RULE<br />\n最後比賽評9:0<br />\n贏比賽之餘老闆都要輸錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbilibili有動畫版睇<br />\n有時間可以睇下 而且唔係好多集<br />\n唔熟棒球規則都睇得"},{"pid":"28970684875f47b9e1ec5d6ff5eb93b0519ba02f","tid":181900,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蛭魔=戰術+心理<br />\n渡久地除左依D  仲有投球技術</blockquote><br />\n講到蛭魔唔識投球咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   蛭魔可唔可以一個人屈柒對面成隊?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果一個人屈柒對面隊 咁仲有咩好睇？<br />\n加上衝鋒廿一個重心唔只係蛭魔<br />\n<br />\n利申 剩係有睇衝鋒廿一</blockquote><br />\n其實我覺得又唔exactly係一個carry,前期你可以咁講，不過後期佢都有靠其實人(管平倉井梅域加),雖然佢地都算係渡久地激發出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得